import React from 'react'
import {Navbar, Nav, NavDropdown} from 'react-bootstrap'

export default class NavBar extends React.Component{
    render(){
        return (
            <Navbar bg="info" expand="lg">
                <Navbar.Brand href="#home">Find My Pup</Navbar.Brand>
                <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                    <NavDropdown title="Sort By Price" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Highest to Lowest</NavDropdown.Item>
                        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">Lowest to Highest</NavDropdown.Item>
                    </NavDropdown>
                    <Nav className="mr-auto">
                    <Nav.Link href="#home">My Pup Cart</Nav.Link>
                    </Nav>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Navbar>
        )
    }
}
